data.description: *ASK AGENT ABOUT INCENTIVES ON THIS HOME!* This charming 3-bed, 2-bath property w/a 2-car garage exudes comfort & style. Inside, you'll find an inviting living room & soothing palette that pairs beautifully with tasteful wood look floors & soft carpeting. The spacious great room is perfect for gatherings. Impeccable kitchen features wood cabinets, granite counters, stainless steel appliances, and a breakfast bar for quick midnight snacks. A home office awaits behind a double door opening of the den. The main bedroom boasts a walk-in closet and private bathroom w/dual sinks for convenience. The lovely backyard provides a relaxing covered patio & a sparkling blue pool, promising endless summer fun. What are you waiting for?
